<h1><span id="Jerome_Gambit">Jerome Gambit</span></h1>
<h2><span id="4._Bxf7.2B.3F"></span><span id="4._Bxf7+?">4. Bxf7+?</span></h2>
<p>White's plan is to lure black's King into the open. This gambit is relatively weak because black can deflect any attack while maintaining a significant material advantage. The obvious response is Kxf7.
</p>
<p><b>1. e4 e5 2. Nf3 Nc6 3. Bc4 Bc5 4. Bxf7</b>
